flowRoot.flowPara: "A single place to work with all your data, and keep it under your control. Integrating features from your apps and services as micro-tools, that can work together in your workflow."

text.tspan: IT ALL STARTED FROM AN IDEA

flowRoot.flowPara: Right now, tools are like salads on a menu, with the ingredients already decided for you and a limited set of options.
WishSalad, however, is like a salad bar where you can combine the ingredients any way you wish.
Integrating all your tools and data in a single place allows you to be more productive.
But it's not less important to have control over your tools and data.
Ensure that you can still access and use your data in the future, even if the services and applications are different than the ones you are using today.
You don't have to choose between privacy and convenience anymore.
Ensure that you can still access and use your data in the future.
Don't choose between privacy and convenience anymore.
And even do new things you didn't know were possible.
